{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-product-details-js","path":"/product/48/","result":{"data":{"strapiProduct":{"content":{"medias":[],"data":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>**搪瓷级钛白粉：**是采用先进的硫酸法工艺生产的，具有纯度高、杂质少、颗粒细小而均匀、有着很强的折射率和较高的消色力，再瓷釉中作乳浊剂，具有很强的乳浊剂和不透明性，使涂搪后涂层薄、光滑和耐酸性强，主要用于搪瓷工业。  </p>\n<p><strong>一、主要标准及特性</strong></p>\n<table class=\"ck-table-resized\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:11.71%;\"><col style=\"width:88.29%;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td style=\"background-color:rgb(170, 170, 170);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\">化学物质</td><td style=\"background-color:rgb(170, 170, 170);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">二氧化钛 (TiO2 )/ 锐钛型</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"background-color:rgb(187, 187, 187);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">产品状态</p></td><td style=\"background-color:rgb(187, 187, 187);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">白色粉末</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"background-color:rgb(204, 204, 204);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">包 装</p></td><td style=\"background-color:rgb(204, 204, 204);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">25kg 编织袋， 1000kg 大袋</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"background-color:rgb(170, 170, 170);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">产品主要特点</p></td><td style=\"background-color:rgb(170, 170, 170);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">用硫酸法工艺生产的锐钛型钛白粉，具有纯度高、杂质少、颗粒细小而均匀、有着很强的折射率和较高的消色力等优点。</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"background-color:rgb(187, 187, 187);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">应用范围</p></td><td style=\"background-color:rgb(187, 187, 187);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">搪瓷工业。</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"background-color:rgb(204, 204, 204);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">企业标准:</p></td><td style=\"background-color:rgb(204, 204, 204);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Calibri;\">Q/IBEY2-2004</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"background-color:rgb(170, 170, 170);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">网络实名</p></td><td style=\"background-color:rgb(170, 170, 170);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">二氧化钛</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><strong>二、质量指标</strong>  </p>\n<table class=\"ck-table-resized\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:11.13%;\"><col style=\"width:57.14%;\"><col style=\"width:16.16%;\"><col style=\"width:15.57%;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 229, 0);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:35px;\">序 号</span></td><td style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 229, 0);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:35px;\">项 目</span></p></td><td style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 229, 0);border:1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);padding:5px 10px;